issues.actaulResult: Below are cases I tried:   1  {code}s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?pr=12347,13000&ba=10&be=1&priceType=FIXED {code}  - works    bapi call: {code}GET /v1/ads?creationDateZoomOutDays=1&url=/s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?pr%3D12347,13000&ba=10&be=1&priceType=FIXED{code}   2  {code}s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?be=1&pr=12347,13000&ba=10&priceType=FIXED {code} - doesn't work, only defference is queries's order  bapi call: {code}GET /v1/ads?creationDateZoomOutDays=1&url=/s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?be%3D1&pr=12347,13000&ba=10&priceType=FIXED{code}   3 {code}s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?be=1&pr=12347,13000 {code}  - doesn't work although without price type,   {code}s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?priceType=FIXED{code} - works  so I think it not related with pricetype but query orders    4 {code}s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?be=6&pr=12347,13000&ba=44{code} - be work but pr/ba don't work  {code}s-venta-inmuebles/cuauhtemoc-df/departamento/v1c1097l10270a1dwp1?ba=44&pr=12347,13000&be=1{code} - ba works, but pr/be don't work    so the conclusion is that: all query parameters after pr don't work in searchSeoUrl if pr is not the first query parameter

issues.actaulResult: The spacing between the top of the intentions menu (including the "hola..." words) and the bottom of the global navigation, and the bottom of the intentions menu and the top of the "desarrollo label box" is not even at very large resolutions.  Currently, there is about 62px of height on top, and 147px on bottom if the browser is large.
issues.expectedResult: The spacing should be the same between the top of the banner and the intentions menu regardless of screen size, and the top of the desarrollo label box and the bottom of the intentions menu.  The implementation looks a bit taller than the original comp, but as long as there is even spacing, the exact pixels don't matter.
